      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://kids.kiddle.co/Germantown_(CDP),_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "New York State Route 9G cuts through Germantown, linking the town north to Hudson and south to Annandale-on-Hudson.",
